### ============================================================
### 11. CLIENTES — /api/client
### ============================================================

### Crear cliente → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/client HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Cliente Reforma",
  "cif": "B11111111",
  "email": "reforma@reforma.com",
  "phone": "611999888",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle de la Reforma",
    "number": "45",
    "postal": "46001",
    "city": "Valencia",
    "province": "Comunidad Valenciana"
  }
}

###

### Sin compañía asociada → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/client HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Cliente Sin Empresa",
  "cif": "B99999999"
}

###

### CIF duplicado en la misma compañía → 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/client HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Otro con mismo CIF",
  "cif": "B12345678"
}

###

### Listar clientes (paginación por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/client HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar con paginación y filtro por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?page=1&limit=5&name=López HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar con ordenación
GET {{baseUrl}}/client?sort=-createdAt HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Obtener cliente por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ID inexistente → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/000000000000000000000000 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Actualizar cliente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "phone": "611999888",
  "email": "nike@nike.com"
}

###

### Soft delete → archived: true
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}}?soft=true HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Hard delete → elimina de MongoDB
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/client/{{clientId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar clientes archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/archived HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Restaurar cliente archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/client/69eb2cd91018dc2325cf577f/restore HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Sin token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/client HTTP/1.1

### ============================================================
### 12. PROYECTOS — /api/project
### ============================================================

### Crear proyecto → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/project HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "name": "Reforma Chalet",
  "projectCode": "PROY-001",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle de la Reforma",
    "number": "45",
    "postal": "46001",
    "city": "Valencia",
    "province": "Comunidad Valenciana"
  },
  "email": "reforma@reforma.com",
  "notes": "Acceso por la puerta principal"
}

###

### Listar proyectos
GET {{baseUrl}}/project HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?client={{clientId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar por nombre y activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?name=Reforma&active=true HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar con paginación y orden
GET {{baseUrl}}/project?page=1&limit=5&sort=-createdAt HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Obtener proyecto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Actualizar proyecto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "notes": "Acceso por puerta principal a partir del lunes",
  "active": false
}

###

### Soft delete proyecto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}?soft=true HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Hard delete proyecto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar proyectos archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/project/archived HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Restaurar proyecto archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/project/{{projectId}}/restore HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ============================================================
### 13. ALBARANES — /api/deliverynote
### ============================================================

### Crear albarán de horas → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "format": "hours",
  "description": "Instalación eléctrica planta baja",
  "workDate": "2025-04-20",
  "hours": 8,
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Carlos Martínez", "hours": 5 },
    { "name": "Ana Gómez", "hours": 3 }
  ]
}

###

### Crear albarán de material → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "format": "material",
  "description": "Entrega de cemento",
  "workDate": "2025-04-20",
  "material": "Cemento Portland",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "sacos"
}

###

### Listar albaranes
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar por proyecto
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?project={{projectId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar por cliente y formato
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?client={{clientId}}&format=hours HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Filtrar firmados
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?signed=true HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Listar con paginación y orden
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=5&sort=-workDate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Obtener albarán por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Descargar PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/pdf/{{deliveryNoteId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Eliminar albarán no firmado → 200
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Firmar albarán (usar Postman)
### Method: PATCH
### URL: http://localhost:3000/api/deliverynote/ALBARAN_ID/sign
### Header: Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
### Body: form-data → key=signature, type=File, value=firma.png

